## YOUR TASK

Given the full text of an academic article, extract all fields specified below as a single JSON object. Complete the `thinking_chain_of_thought` field FIRST, before completing any other field. Do not add, rename, or omit any fields. Follow all extraction rules exactly. Every confidence field uses the 0–10 integer scale defined below.

